captions.text: "Masking"
I was too scared to even knock.

You're hopeless. You just walk right up to
her, and say 'I want to go out with you!'
I'd feel like a fool.
She's... just way too beautiful.
Hello, Timothy.
Hey there... Rosie... I'm here to visit Kid.
Hi, Kid. What's up?
Hi, Tim.
Is Rosie going to take you out later?
She is.

That's good. I need your help. Could
you ask her... if... well, you know, maybe

if she likes me at all? I'll be nearby...
But... I'll wear a cool disguise.

That sounds awesome. Disguises
are always really fun.

Thank you, Kid. Thanks. I'm just
too shy to do it by myself.

Oh, I'll tell you more. No, I'm serious.
She totally said it. I know, right...
Kid, come on!

Exactly! I thought she must have been joking.
But she actually wore it. Yeah, yeah. That's

right. I think we're ready. Just ask the
questions, and I'll listen to the answers.
Rosie, I was wondering. Do you like Tim
...wondering if you like ti-... tickling people?

Sure. I guess I like it. But I'm trying to talk.
Why don't you... go play on the slide?

Sorry... so where were we? Yeah.
It's just so beige.

I wouldn't be caught
dead in a beige collar...

You can't just come right out and say my name.
You should be a little sneaky.

Oh yeah, they're way fake. Hey, Kid.
Who are you talking to over there?
The... Magic snowman?

I'm here. Yeah, there's no way she is part
shar pei. Shih tzu, maybe. I mean does she

actually think she's impressing us? Wait a sec.
Don't forget. You've got to be sneaky.
What is up with you, Kid?

Rosie, ... You know how there are
other people in the world?

There are more people in the
world than our family, right?
Uh, yeah.

Well among these other people... One
of them... might ... fall... in love...

Look, Kid. When I get off the phone...
I promise I'll play with you lots.

Alright? Until then, why don't you get
on the merry-go-round. I'll push it.

Yeah, sorry. I'm back. She's always been weird.
But she's got really great clothes...
That is an awesome disguise, Tim!

Culottes make my knees look stupid.
Aww, aren't you sweet! I always thought

you looked awesome in jodhpurs. Maybe
I will give lederhosen a try then.

I mean why not? Timothy? Why
are you inside a snowman?
Because.

So! I'm very happy that you came along!
Why don't you stay and play with us?

Tim! This has been so very fun!
I like you a lot, you know.

I like you as well, Rosie. I was
always just too scared to say it.
